  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced ginger and garlic, stir-fry for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Include red chili peppers and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add chicken breast pieces and soy sauce. Stir well to coat the meat with flavors.",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low, add cornstarch water mixture (cornstarch dissolved in a little water) and stir continuously for about 2 minutes or until thickened.",
    "Mix sesame seeds into the dish and cook for another minute.",
    "Season with salt and lime juice to taste. Stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Serve hot."
